title: Episode #10: Man Stories with Carlos Infante
description: Welcome back to another episode of The Art of Manliness podcast! We took a short break because of the Thanksgiving holiday, but we're back with another edition of Man Stories. In this episode we talk to Carlos Infante of Mexico City, Mexico and ask him what it means to be a man.
author: contact@artofmanliness.com (The Art of Manliness)
